Class AbstractWorkoutStatsFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InWorkoutFragment, PreWorkoutFragment

    public abstract class AbstractWorkoutStatsFragment
extends NavigableFragment
    This class is parent for workout stats bases fragments. Both pre-workout and in-workout. It contains basic listeners and bottom sheet related functionality.
